<sect2 id="Treefoot"><title>Treefoot</title>
<para>A <code>treefoot </code>is main part of tree which contains set of footers. The set of footers is defined by a number of <code>treefooter </code>components, one for each column. Each column will appear as a footer at the bottom of the tree.</para>
